<h2>MISSION</h2>

To satisfy our customer’s needs and surpass their expectations.
To maintain good relationships with our local service providers like hotel owners, staff, tour coordinators, and drivers.
To value our guests’ needs above all else and give them the best vacation experience.
To provide our guests with as much information as they need regarding the places they’ll visit.

<h2>VISION</h2>

To become the Philippines’ leading tour operator that provides excellent and innovative travel services to our guests.
To be able to introduce and promote Philippine tourism.
To help preserve and maintain our country’s natural resources the best we can.
<br><br><br><br>

<b><i>Our expertise in the travel industry, our company became a prolific supplier, and strengthening our partnership with our tour operators both International and Domestic, Astrokidd Travel Tours is now confidently providing its clients a variety of travel services that they pertinently need at the time they require it at minimum cost.</i></b>
